messages.content: /generate AutoClaim Defender — A simple and safe Minecraft protection plugin that automatically claims a configurable area of land (such as nearby chunks) when a player places their first chest, crafting table, or furnace, helping prevent accidental or unwanted changes by others. Admin tools allow for safe moderation, and optional economy support can limit or manage additional claims — making it ideal for friendly survival or casual servers."
